57

00:03:25,250  -->  00:03:29,010
Something else to keep in mind with strings is that they are immutable.

58

00:03:29,010  -->  00:03:34,130
We cannot change a character in the string as each character within the string is set,

59

00:03:34,130  -->  00:03:38,210
